    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_18_647-1018",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "647-1018",
      "markText": "盛神中有五气，神为之长，心为之舍，德为之大，养神之所归诸道。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=647&rangeEnd=1018",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=647&rangeEnd=1018"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_5_5697-5715",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5697-5715",
      "markText": "别人在说话，是动；自己沉默不说，是静",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5697&rangeEnd=5715",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5697&rangeEnd=5715"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_3_9122-9167",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9122-9167",
      "markText": "正是因为《鬼谷子》是这样确立“纵横”理论的，所以，在儒学取得统治地位后，纵横之学即被排斥。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9122&rangeEnd=9167",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9122&rangeEnd=9167"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_4_13630-13639",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "13630-13639",
      "markText": "为小无内，为大无外",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=13630&rangeEnd=13639",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=13630&rangeEnd=13639"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_6_6450-6465",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6450-6465",
      "markText": "乃揣切时宜，从便所为，以求其变",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6450&rangeEnd=6465",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6450&rangeEnd=6465"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_10_6532-6770",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "6532-6770",
      "markText": "常有事于人，人莫能先，先事而生，此最难为",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6532&rangeEnd=6770",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6532&rangeEnd=6770"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_12_7647-7844",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "7647-7844",
      "markText": "是故智者不用其所短，而用愚人之所长，不用其所拙，而用愚人之所工，故不困也",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=7647&rangeEnd=7844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=7647&rangeEnd=7844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_13_8804-9015",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "8804-9015",
      "markText": "无以人之所不欲而强之于人，无以人之所不知而教之于人。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8804&rangeEnd=9015",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=8804&rangeEnd=9015"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_26_821-851",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "821-851",
      "markText": "在考察时须注意，若遇到那种目不斜视，耳不旁听之人，则须小心。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=851",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=821&rangeEnd=851"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_3_6233-6312",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "6233-6312",
      "markText": "捭阖》云：“夫贤不肖智愚勇怯有差，乃可捭，乃可阖；乃可进，乃可退；乃可贱，乃可贵，无为以牧之。”这里的“无为”是指顺从游说对象的性格特点而施以不同的游说手段。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6233&rangeEnd=6312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=6233&rangeEnd=6312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_4_5153-5319",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5153-5319",
      "markText": "夫贤不肖、智愚、勇怯有差",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5153&rangeEnd=5319",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5153&rangeEnd=5319"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_5_725-808",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "725-808",
      "markText": "关于反应术之原理：因为任何事都有“阴阳”，也就都有反覆。反，谓反观对方；覆，谓审察自己。反，反过来站在对方立场看问题；覆，站在对方立场看问题后，再审察自己现在的做法。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300090817&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=725&rangeEnd=808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f44326c0813ab89f9g017037?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=725&rangeEnd=808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300090817_5_1717-1770",
